ps://na.cx/i/shUaEV6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshUaEV6.png&h=e526e96d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n美國國旗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2jBAws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2jBAws.jpg&h=4a7ca054&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"why黑藍黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"黑:流水<br />\n藍:本土<br />\n黃:雨傘"},{"pid":"5fd02e91a3078a9adb9c85c52ee4901647aeeac4","tid":1557272,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"P 俾超額發唔到Post，please help <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.15 係「國際民主日」，點解完全無活動Post? </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據《世界人權宣言》第二十一條第（三）款﹕「人民的意志是政府權力的基礎」<br />\n9.15係聯合國嘅「國際民主日」，2019年主題「參與」，重申民主係「以人為中心」。(官網﹕<a href=\"https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fzh%2Fevents%2Fdemocracyday%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ec2bc8a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/</a> (得殘體字sorry) ) <br />\n<br />\n我哋依定係對抗緊極權，爭取緊雙普選，呢個咁有象徵意義嘅日子點可以唔做嘢? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本地應該要搞大遊行，本來民陣前兩日都話申請緊</span>，但警方唔回應就完全無哂聲氣。<span style=\"color: red;\">海外集會要再次港、藏、疆合作</span>，甚至聯繫埋全世界受壓迫地區嘅人一齊發聲。<br />\n<br />\n6.12、721、811、831&hellip;全部都要勝利之後先可以查明真相，如果唔係有再多嘅證據，未來都只會變成野史。請大家化憤怒為創意同行動吧！世界領袖讚賞我哋嘅，係呢場運動嘅靈活多變，不忘同世界連軌。而我地亦已成功將呢場運動變成<span style=\"color: red;\">自由世界VS極權嘅抗爭</span>。我哋唔想成為國際怨婦，就要令更加多人明白This is <span style=\"color: red;\">NOT ONLY a protest for Hong Kong people but for the sake of the World! </span><br />\n<br />\nAttention! 依家正苦係咁用衝突黎分化我哋同世界建立既信任。請大家要好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Free Hong Kong <br />\nAnti Chinazi </span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1. 之前有巴打寫﹕If we burn, the world burns  有無人留咗record ? <br />\n2. 回顧9.4 「2019年中美關係回顧」聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-09-05%2F70001880&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=e723661d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880</a>"},{"pid":"f1f159bd4c0ff9458c99f7f5bf0ebd34f34e488e","tid":1557272,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"有冇紀念911活動？"},{"pid":"12b41f79ea8598e41c1416b05f058425384321b8","tid":1557272,"uid":192456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f159bd4c0ff9458c99f7f5bf0ebd34f34e488e","tid":1557272,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"有冇紀念911活動？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5806af5701cfb8aef63c8f2d0b9cb8995f2d7","tid":1557272,"uid":170014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"應該暫停圍狗屋，<br />\n全力痴牆做文宣，唔限定本身嘅連儂位置，<br />\n務求全街都係。<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己諗吓，幾百人圍狗屋有用，<br />\n定幾百人每人痴30張文宣，<br />\n當你500x30，條街一晚就多15000張文宣。<br />\n仲要係every where，唔限喺連儂區。<br />\n運動要有新鮮感，你哋日日圍狗屋，大家都睇到悶。<br />\n而家要搵啲新野，重新吸引返大眾嘅attention 。"},{"pid":"b198d8e43f95448e94bca18fa07153a4f31e48db","tid":1557272,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"一出事<br />\n法案玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要睇實班鬼"},{"pid":"3042c9acc604eb732579c552b0521ae72530111f","tid":1557272,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f159bd4c0ff9458c99f7f5bf0ebd34f34e488e","tid":1557272,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"有冇紀念911活動？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"當年911訪問既既就係Trump"},{"pid":"abe33f0cbc4f92dcfd65272648f765418ea8